Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.98,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I started a game on the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:08.38,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,It’s called the "Mouse Game". You sell tickets to your friends and make money.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.22,0:00:12.88,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,But if I start making lots of money, the other players will have a grudge against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:18.72,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,There will be people who want to kill me then, so I have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:27.34,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,At first I thought this was just a game, but it made me feel bad after a while, and I wanted to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:34.10,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,There was a questionnaire that came with the game asking me what I thought of it, so I wrote the company telling them what I honestly thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:36.98,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I guess they know who I am now and don’t like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:38.64,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I’m sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:41.98,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I don’t like games like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.36,0:00:45.52,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I’d rather play a game that everyone can laugh with and enjoy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:47.72,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,It isn’t for me.
